---
/**
 * Giscus comment component.
 * Configure at https://giscus.app/ and update the attributes below.
 * Requires enabling GitHub Discussions on the repo.
 */
---

<section class="mt-16 pt-8 border-t border-border">
  <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-6">评论</h2>
  <div id="giscus-container">
    <script
      is:inline
      src="https://giscus.app/client.js"
      data-repo="xirain/techlearn"
      data-repo-id=""
      data-category="Announcements"
      data-category-id=""
      data-mapping="pathname"
      data-strict="0"
      data-reactions-enabled="1"
      data-emit-metadata="0"
      data-input-position="top"
      data-theme="preferred_color_scheme"
      data-lang="zh-CN"
      data-loading="lazy"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
      async
    ></script>
  </div>
  <p class="text-xs text-muted-foreground mt-4">
    评论系统基于 <a href="https://giscus.app" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-primary hover:underline">Giscus</a>，
    需要启用仓库的 GitHub Discussions 后配置 repo-id 和 category-id。
  </p>
</section>
